
This is a demo video placeholder.
In a real implementation, place your actual demo.mp4 file here.
The file should be a valid MP4 video file compatible with HTML5 video players.

For testing purposes, you can:
1. Download a sample video from: https://sample-videos.com/
2. Use any MP4 video file you have
3. Create a simple video using ffmpeg or similar tools

Example ffmpeg command to create a test video:
ffmpeg -f lavfi -i testsrc=duration=10:size=320x240:rate=1 demo.mp4
